Title: Authorizes the city of Poughkeepsie to alienate and discontinue the use of certain parklands
Summary: Authorizes the city of Poughkeepsie to alienate and discontinue the use of certain parklands for the purpose of constructing a new emergency services communications tower.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to authorizing the city of Poughkeepsie to alienate and discontinue the use of certain parklands
